graph TB
    VectorSize["VECTOR_SIZE<br/>Environment Variable"]
    QdrantCollection["Qdrant Collection<br/>Vector Configuration"]
    EmbeddingProvider["Embedding Provider<br/>generate_embedding()"]
    
    VectorSize -->|must match| QdrantCollection
    VectorSize -->|configures| EmbeddingProvider
    
